(5, 1, '2010-09-22 16:33:56', '2010-09-22 16:33:56', 'The Church of Our Redeemer meets according to the following schedule:\r\n<table border="0" width="100%">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2">\r\n<h3>SUNDAY</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="20%">8am</td>\r\n<td>Holy Eucharist, Contemplative Service (no music, no childcare)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>10am</td>\r\n<td>Holy Eucharist, Main Service - music, childcare, Sunday school</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>11:15am</td>\r\n<td>Coffee Hour</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Men''s Bible Study, after main service 2nd Sunday of each month</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2">\r\n<h3>MONDAY</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="20%">3pm - 7pm</td>\r\n<td>Pastor''s Scheduled Open Door</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2">\r\n<h3>WEDNESDAY</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="20%">8am</td>\r\n<td>Holy Eucharist with Litany of Healing and open discussion of lessons</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="20%">9:30am</td>\r\n<td>Women''s Bible Study</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="20%">7pm</td>\r\n<td>Bible Study</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2">\r\n<h3>THURSDAY</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="20%">7:30pm</td>\r\n<td>Choir Practice</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Snow Policy: <i>Our snow policy is this - if it is physically possible for the rector to get to the church on any given day, there will be a service. (He has a 4WD, and he knows how to use it!)  The fact that there is a service, however, does NOT mean that you should come if you don''t feel completely safe. Believe us when we say, God doesn''t take attendance. Please, use your good judgement when deciding if you really want to brave the snow.</i></p>\r\n<p>If conditions are such that we don''t want peeople to come to the church, the answering machine message will be changed to advise you of that fact. Please call the church office at (703)327-4060 if you are in doubt.</P', 'Schedule of Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'schedule-of-services', '', '', '2010-09-25 21:08:02', '2010-09-25 21:08:02', '', 0, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch.com/?page_id=5', 0, 'page', '', 0),
