(47, 1, '2010-09-22 17:54:06', '2010-09-22 17:54:06', 'Part of being disciple is learning the discipline of service. If you''re unsure of how to start, why not start by being an usher?\r\n\r\nBeing an usher requires no preparation or commitment outside of the service, and yet it is the first contact that most members will have as they join the church. Responsibilities boil down to greeting people with the joy you already have, giving them a bulletin, and bringing up the communion elements after announcements.  It''s easy but important. \r\n\r\nIf you''re ready to sign up, please contact John Sheehan at (703)327-4060.', 'We need ushers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'we-need-ushers', '', '', '2010-09-23 16:01:03', '2010-09-23 16:01:03', '', 0, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch.com/?p=47', 0, 'post', '', 0),
