(107, 1, '2010-09-23 13:55:46', '2010-09-23 13:55:46', 'The Church of Our Redeemer is located on Route 50 (John Mosby Highway) in the village of Aldie at 39518 John Mosby Highway ·  Aldie, VA 20105. The church is 1 mile west of the traffic circle where Route 15 (north to Leesburg, south to Haymarket) and Route 50 (west to Middleburg, east to South Riding) intersect.  For directions, click here or look at the map below.\r\nFrom South Riding, head west on Route 50, past the three traffic circles. The church will be on your right.\r\nFrom Leesburg, head south on 15, turn right onto Route 50. The church will be on your right.\r\nFrom Haymarket, I-66, and points south, head north on 15, go 3/4 around the traffic circle onto Route 50 west. The church will be on your right.\r\nFrom Middleburg and points west, head east on Route 50, past Snickersville Turnpike, and through Aldie. The church will be on your left.', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '107', '', '', '2010-09-23 13:55:46', '2010-09-23 13:55:46', '', 0, 'http://doverknoll.com/aldiechurch/?p=107', 7, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
